{"tid":210312,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[05:40] 希古恩：很抱歉又在大賽中連累美斯出局","createTime":"2017-04-20T22:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T01:30:28.000Z","uid":28938,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a656bf46de00179418806315d3a1d163a29dd76c","tid":210312,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T22:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0HQ887q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0HQ887q.jpg&h=7d1ff049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>希古恩：很抱歉又在大賽中拖累美斯出局</strong><br />\n[05:40]主場十七次射門僅一次中框，巴塞兩回合均未能射破祖雲達斯，無緣晉級歐聯四強。賽後希古恩於訪問中指，對於數次國際性大賽均拖累美斯出局感到歉意。<br />\n<br />\n於接受Sky Sport訪問時，希古恩首先指出斑馬軍團防守力實在出眾︰「對手可能是最強的球隊，晉級令我們更自信，我真的不敢相信在魯營零封對手。」<br />\n<br />\n他同時亦表示：「作為一個隊友或對手，很抱歉無論在國家隊、球會比賽均拖累了美斯出局；他實在值得拿取更高的榮譽；但足球就是這樣，勝利者只有一個。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JF4vx47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJF4vx47.jpg&h=c3ab4cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我與戴巴拿已經商量好了，歐聯決賽前夕將送美斯一款比較舒服的拖鞋，讓他安在家中觀看我們的球賽。」<br />\n<br />\n記者短訊向美斯告之希古恩將送禮物給他，截稿前卻未獲回應。"},{"pid":"590a07fb750aeb03cecc022f86f4c2497bc27863","tid":210312,"uid":83796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T22:27:56.000Z","msg":"退出國家隊"},{"pid":"0caf53567fc67f7fce366e17bd6043a867ea3b42","tid":210312,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T22:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>退出國家隊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉會西班牙國家隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6818c7399f07dfb12c3dc6a7cb738ec7b510181e","tid":210312,"uid":83153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T22:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>退出國家隊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉會西班牙國家隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家先黎轉好柒 況且呢家西班穿都未必贏到wc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e641c599625fc8dbba324720fb398dbd48354b","tid":210312,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:04:46.000Z","msg":"G持清繼續po新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1f973bef35d7723345c47eca34b07d29967ae9","tid":210312,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:12:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>退出國家隊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉會西班牙國家隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家先黎轉好柒 況且呢家西班穿都未必贏到wc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前美斯巴塞carry沙維同小白，今日一樣可以carry 伊斯高同施華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87989491a17d2b05643a1df27b053dc5c4f431a5","tid":210312,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>G持清繼續po新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好東西齊分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67081fade344e9532342fb818de9aa0378712152","tid":210312,"uid":9269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:17:30.000Z","msg":"想學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79353707e337c098a591d78fcb56aa56a59f6826","tid":210312,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eee1d293a1df87c1498efa22dc70326958c9a30","tid":210312,"uid"